description: Returns a list of the frameworks that are available in the Audit Manager framework library.

parameters.name: frameworkType
parameters.description: The type of framework, such as a standard framework or a custom framework.

nested_items.name: frameworkMetadataList
nested_items.description: A list of metadata that the ListAssessmentFrameworks API returns for each framework.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the framework.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the framework.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The framework type, such as a standard framework or a custom framework.

nested_items.name: logo
nested_items.description: The logo that's associated with the framework.

nested_items.name: complianceType
nested_items.description: The compliance type that the new custom framework supports, such as CIS or HIPAA.

nested_items.name: controlsCount
nested_items.description: The number of controls that are associated with the framework.

nested_items.name: controlSetsCount
nested_items.description: The number of control sets that are associated with the framework.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time when the framework was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the framework was most recently updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.
